        "| Task | Formula logic | Example |\n",
        "|---|---|---|\n",
        "| Future value | `=PV*(1+r)^n` | `=1000*(1+0.08)^2` |\n",
        "| Present value | `=FV/(1+r)^n` | `=1000/(1+0.08)^2` |\n",
        "| FVIF | `=(1+r)^n` | `=(1+0.08)^2` |\n",
