        "\n",
        "## 17. Practice questions\n",
        "\n",
        "### Short-answer questions\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Why is OMR 1 today worth more than OMR 1 next year?\n",
        "2. What is the difference between simple interest and compound interest?\n",
        "3. What does FVIF measure?\n",
        "4. What does PVIF measure?\n",
        "5. What happens to present value when the discount rate increases?\n",
        "\n",
        "### Applied questions\n",
        "\n",
        "1. A farmer invests OMR 2,500 for 3 years at 7% compound interest. Calculate the future value.\n",
        "\n",
        "2. A farmer will receive OMR 6,000 after 4 years. The discount rate is 9%. Calculate the present value.\n",
        "\n",
        "3. A buyer offers OMR 3,000 today or OMR 3,400 after one year. If the discount rate is 10%, which option is better?\n",
        "\n",
        "4. A farmer borrows OMR 4,000 for 2 years at 5% simple interest. Calculate total repayment.\n",
        "\n",
        "5. A farmer saves OMR 1,200 today at 6% annual compound interest. How much will it become after 5 years?\n",
        "\n",
